text: Rene Tschernitschek (born 30 March 1977) is a German gymnast. He competed in six events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Halle (Saale)
